    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ceramic ware manufactured since the mid-18th century in Thuringia, Germany. The works consists of predominently hard-paste porcelain tableware, often in a Baroque style.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
